abstract: An agreement between college counselors and the Justice Department should free up colleges to woo early-decision applicants with financial aid.

abstract: President Jair Bolsonaro of Brazil said Mr. Trump decided not to pursue tariffs on Brazilian steel after a phone call on Friday.
snippet: President Jair Bolsonaro of Brazil said Mr. Trump decided not to pursue tariffs on Brazilian steel after a phone call on Friday.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON â€” President Trump has backed off a threat he made this month to impose tariffs on Brazilian metal, a move that would have broken a previous agreement with the country and risked reigniting trade tensions.
